yingyinNormal.en: We're leading the coalition to degrade and ultimately destroy ISIL.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们领导着削弱并最终摧毁ISIL组织的联盟。

yingyinNormal.en: But those decisions are ultimately mine. I will not make them lightly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是最终都是由我决定的，我不会轻易做决定。

yingyinNormal.en: America is leading the world in the fight to degrade and ultimately destroy the terrorist group known as ISIL.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国正在领导着世界，削弱并最终摧毁像ISIL这样的恐怖组织。

yingyinNormal.en: Ultimately, for full satisfaction, it requires plain sight. Additionally, serial killers are easily profiled.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最终，为了满足感，它得暴露在众目睽睽之下。并且，连环杀手特点突出。

yingyinNormal.en: Darling, I hired these people for their expertise, and ultimately, they feel that we would be doing the brand a disservice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，我雇这些人来给我专业意见，最终，他们觉得我们是在为这个品牌帮倒忙。

yingyinNormal.en: The troops I'll visit on Monday have been part of our mission to degrade and ultimately destroy ISIL in Iraq and Syria.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我周一要慰问的部队，曾经参与了我们削弱并最终摧毁在伊拉克和叙利亚的ISIL组织的任务。

yingyinNormal.en: Penny, this is your enterprise, so it's ultimately your decision, but based on the quality of his work, I'd strongly recommend that we let Leonard go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮，这是你的公司，所以最终决议权在于你，但基于他工作的质量，我强烈建议开除莱纳德。

yingyinNormal.en: So it's actually extremely high amount of negativity fear and anxiety about China, Sino-phobia that I think is not just misinformed but also misleading, and ultimately dangerous, very dangerous.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，有大量的对中国负面的恐慌和焦虑中国恐惧症，我认为这不仅是错误的消息，还造成了误导，最终是危险的非常危险。

yingyinNormal.en: And you can see that everyone is so focused and the concentration I can feel, the buzz in the room, because I guess they have to, they are ultimately responsible for every train that passes through.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里每个人都全神贯注，屋里嗡嗡作响，我能感受到那专注的气氛，我想，他们必须要聚精会神，他们为每辆经过的列车负最终责任。

yingyinNormal.en: The two sides of the updating story are ultimately quite consistent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这两种改变印象的故事在最后都满有关联性。

yingyinNormal.en: As with all of life's decisions, what you do with them is ultimately up to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 像其他生活中的决定一样，你怎么利用法则最后都取决于你。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, ultimately, I was trying you know, I wanted tell him you know, that I'm still in love with him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实我想，我打算告诉他我还爱他。

yingyinNormal.en: Does it matter? You're ultimately just gonna die or get divorced or have to blow your pets head off. Aghh. Me too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有关系吗？你始终都会死，或离婚，或枪杀你的宠物。我也是。

yingyinNormal.en: If a player scores a goal, it ultimately has a stronger impact on your impression of their skills than if they miss the net.
yingyinNormal.zh: 足球员射门得分，这最后会有个更强的影响加深你对他们球技的印象，比起他们没有得分的话。

yingyinNormal.en: Or it tracks back to arbitrary axiomatic statements, or it's ultimately circular, i.e. I'm moving out because I'm moving out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要么就是能从所谓偶然的公理陈述中，找到答案也有可能是终极循环，也就是说，因为我要搬出去，所以我要搬出去。

yingyinNormal.en: So we're staying vigilant. And we're moving ahead with our strategy to degrade and ultimately destroy this terrorist organization.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，我们要保持警惕。而且我们也正在实施我们的战略，逐步打击直至完全消灭这一恐怖组织。

yingyinNormal.en: Whatever ventures I might pursue would be to make clear that what unites us is ultimately far more redeeming and compelling than anything that separates me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论我追求的是什么，我都会明确，将我们团结在一起的信念终将远远胜过拆散我们的一切事物。

yingyinNormal.en: Whether it's to degrade and ultimately destroy a group of terrorists or to contain and combat a threat like the Ebola epidemic in Africa, we ask a lot of our troops.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论是打击和消灭恐怖组织，还是抗击非洲的埃博拉病毒，我们都动用了大量的军队。

yingyinNormal.en: Over the past week, the United States has continued to lead our friends and allies in the strategy to degrade and ultimately destroy the terrorist group known as ISIL.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过去一周，合众国带领盟友一起实施打击直至消灭ISIL组织的战略。

yingyinNormal.en: But ultimately, it was a disruption on top of a disruption. It was Bob Metcalfe inventing the Ethernet and the connection of all these computers that fundamentally changed everything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过，最令人措手不及的还是鲍勃·梅得卡夫发明了以太网。电脑的联网，革命性地改变了一切。
